        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/da6949/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-07-29T01:43:55.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"284493\">\n<blockquote>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"284493\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>\u2026 but I take it there will not be so many more\u2026</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Are they not making this anymore? I still see their regular CdNV around.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I believe he is retiring.  I can\u2019t find the source for where I heard that, so maybe someone will correct me. But I have it in my head that there will be no more soon.</p>",
